55;\"><b>주문</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-767097d9-a1be-4105-8455-a51c3155a110\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> &gt; 주문서작성 &gt; 주문서 확인 &gt; 견적서 제출 &gt; 결제요청 &gt; </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-94f56ede-8b94-4266-a07f-6291f7fb8cfa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>결제확인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c487247-5490-4a20-bd5d-f56309edba77\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> &gt; 디자인작업 &gt; 디자인 교정 &gt; </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-13bfdb76-9010-4f1b-bf0f-2c9650699914\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인 컨펌</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88ae5ba0-c0b7-41e2-b5c1-7e17632c3e5c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> &gt; </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-559e1cd1-864a-4d36-8a80-6acc504d245f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄작업 &gt; 후가공 작업</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eedeaef6-3d38-47aa-a00e-15672a1232a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> &gt; 배송시작 &gt; </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-42841559-38ad-422f-9a36-e2ca0497174b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>배송완료</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-198aeab7-60cb-4628-b22a-e00ac5b3d008\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> &gt; 구매확정 &gt; </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-1d1107e8-6bd0-47a7-9e1d-b1af9b994114\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>완료</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e4ea002-ea89-4bd6-8860-86ba97a9b3c5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7835bfa4-81ce-4782-891b-f3c48b44e08c\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d158c2c0-b880-41bd-a2f0-c8a7c979cef7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d2430663-c863-4878-94dc-1e6c493f6087\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20c438bb-a369-4edd-a63c-f20a80f6c82e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e4d80cc9-d1bd-4432-95c1-6eadc1d7b33e\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-27ab6615-df1d-46b3-ab31-42ea452f6e53\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-47db7a11-a3bd-4574-89e7-8a9ccb1c2901\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebea83fe-6071-42a6-8f14-432958b70a2c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f6378a52-0403-4160-8bcd-18304ecc88cc\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">간단하게 요약하면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3471060a-da84-4d95-ba77-808293fa8fa7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-cad30e2b-4305-4708-a688-52d995fb208b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주문 &gt; 결제 &gt; 디자인 &gt; 생산 &gt; 납품 &gt; 완료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-caff7797-d36b-4643-9729-929123cbe7b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-afa31276-2dec-4e34-8ef6-75a25c1e30bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22260e7d-5511-42e6-974a-e097b55c650d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-4068b8e7-016d-4bd6-b1c1-3d4a2648f863\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 프로세스와 작업 커뮤니케이션하는 창구가 바로 사이트개발의 개발의미일겁니다. 고객이 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 사이트에서 정보를 검색하고 본인의 취지에 맞는 내용을 서칭한 후에 쌍방이 간편하게 커뮤니케이션하는 그런 창구가 (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e602c31-8009-4ff7-9a36-9645483b7d1d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2c3785fa-006f-4ee7-b31f-fe8924e4b9c5\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01250dc8-874b-48ca-984e-649a8abffe18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d08ebf09-e24c-41a9-89f9-eb7b3034c5da\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-2c5c3656-0e43-437e-849c-8460738e14b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e80ae63-bb43-4aac-a8a3-70c0615d2767\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d7ec9249-9f9c-4899-8e85-a7806417b45b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다음 글의 내용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-884f49d9-5e34-4b31-8deb-ee14cf26e6da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-daaa3c15-fedd-4d7c-ac05-30fa71d878a4\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e3cd7275-8d4f-43bc-933e-62b28c2531a2\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[예시] STEP1 / 명함을 예로 든 메인 페이지 사양 정의, 벤치마킹으로 알아봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ad6aa1bc-83f0-4609-ab59-affd0a46e24f\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8712f0ef-3072-454b-a7a7-81c1f9d50a92\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-col